    <item>
      <title>随着选票不断涌入，小型股在选举之夜涨幅最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/small-caps-post-biggest-election-night-move-as-votes-roll-in</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着主要州投票结束，美国股指期货周二攀升至盘中高点，股市中风险最高的部分出现最大波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/small-caps-post-biggest-election-night-move-as-votes-roll-in</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 04:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2024 年选举之夜：特朗普领先选举人票数</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-06/2024-election-night-trump-leading-electoral-vote-count-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[截至美国东部时间晚上 10:30，唐纳德·特朗普在选举人团投票中以 204 比 112 领先卡玛拉·哈里斯。哈里斯需要在“锈带”取得胜利。特朗普已经在德克萨斯州、佛罗里达州、俄亥俄州、阿拉巴马州、密苏里州和犹他州获胜。宾夕法尼亚州将是今晚的关键。凯莉·莱因茨报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-06/2024-election-night-trump-leading-electoral-vote-count-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 03:59:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国民调结果引发市场恐慌，香港股市和人民币下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/yuan-hong-kong-stocks-slump-as-trump-s-early-lead-fuels-jitters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统大选结果显示唐纳德·特朗普领先，这对人民币和股市造成沉重压力，因为交易员担心贸易紧张局势加剧会产生不良后果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/yuan-hong-kong-stocks-slump-as-trump-s-early-lead-fuels-jitters</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 03:47:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元飙升推动亚洲当局采取货币防御措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/asia-starts-tentative-defence-against-dollar-election-strength</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于选举波动导致美元飙升，导致该地区的货币面临压力，一些亚洲国家当局已开始采取行动保护本币汇率，而其他国家当局则处于待命状态。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/asia-starts-tentative-defence-against-dollar-election-strength</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 03:28:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场预期特朗普胜选，新兴货币暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/emerging-currencies-slump-as-markets-lean-toward-a-trump-victory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新兴市场货币下跌，因为交易员预计唐纳德·特朗普将赢得美国总统大选，这一结果被视为将提振美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/emerging-currencies-slump-as-markets-lean-toward-a-trump-victory</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 03:11:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在美大选中领先，美元走强，铜价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/copper-drops-as-dollar-strengthens-on-early-us-election-results</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于唐纳德·特朗普在美国大选中取得领先，美元上涨，铜价与大多数金属价格一起下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/copper-drops-as-dollar-strengthens-on-early-us-election-results</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 02:54:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普扩大领先优势，美元创 2020 年以来最大涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/dollar-rises-to-highest-since-july-as-polls-close-in-key-states</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国总统大选的初步结果显示唐纳德·特朗普在一些关键州占有优势，市场猜测他的政策将使美国利率维持在高位，从而引发美国国债收益率大幅上升，美元出现了2020年3月以来的最大涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/dollar-rises-to-highest-since-july-as-polls-close-in-key-states</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 02:21:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普交易势头强劲，美国股市和收益率上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球范围内与唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 总统竞选前景上升有关的一系列交易取得了决定性的进展，股指期货延续涨势，美国国债收益率跃升，美元创下 2023 年 2 月以来的最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 23:05:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元延续跌势，特朗普竞选活动推进，日本股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/japanese-stock-futures-edge-higher-before-us-votes-tallied</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国总统大选的早期结果导致一些交易员押注唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 比卡玛拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 更具优势，日本蓝筹股指数上涨逾 3%，而日元跌至 7 月以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/japanese-stock-futures-edge-higher-before-us-votes-tallied</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 22:28:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
